CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 30, 1960, pg. A16 reads: "AKA's Initiate - The initiation of Iota Chapter of Alpha Kappa Alpha Sorority was held at the home of Frances Pace by Virginia Carter Lowe, graduate adviser, and Elaine Lee. Seated, front: Winifred Haddock and Elaine Lee.  Second row: Constance Cottingham, Pat Marlow, Sara Blakey, Virginia Lowe, Norma Boyde and Frances Pace. - Harris Photo"
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of eight members of Iota Chapter of Alpha Kappa Alpha Sorority, seated: Winifred Haddock and Elaine Lee;  second row: Constance Cottingham, Pat Marlow, Sara Blakey, Virginia Lowe, Norma Boyde, and Frances Pace, posed in home of Frances Pace, another version
